src:
【豪門爆姦情1】生日當天收到淫照　元祖少奶安晨妤與老公驚爆婚變
05 Nov 2019, 21:58 by 娛樂組, 攝影組
歌手兼網路電商企業家安晨妤，和「富二代」、元祖食品少東張劭緯結婚13年，表面一副甜蜜幸福模樣，沒想到日前卻驚爆婚變，主因是張劭緯結婚以來，背著老婆安晨妤偷歡數女，還拍下淫照與影片。











據了解，今年8月初，安晨妤飛去上海，原本打算幫老公過父親節，並與兒女見面，享受天倫之樂，沒想到飛到當地後，老公卻消失，然後安晨妤被張家阻在門外，見不到兒女的她相當心急，於是打給張家所有人，卻沒人接她電話，兒女甚至被帶到張劭緯哥哥家中。








更令人心酸的是，安晨妤竟然在今年生日，意外看到老公婚外情性愛照及影片，還有多張老公自拍與外遇女性親密照片，張張不堪入目，讓安晨妤完全崩潰，才知身邊的老公根本不是她所認識的人。
更新時間｜2019.11.06 04:38
text:
[Grandeur smuggling affair 1] received a slut on the day of the birthday Yuanzu Shao's milk An Chen 妤 and her husband broke the marriage
05 Nov 2019, 21:58 by Entertainment Group, Photography Group
The singer and online e-commerce entrepreneur An Chenxi, married the "rich second generation" and Yuanzu food Shaodong Zhang Weiwei for 13 years, with a sweet and happy appearance. I did not expect that the marriage was changed recently. The main reason is that Zhang Weiwei has been married since the beginning. The wife An Chen sneaked a few women, but also photographed pornography and film.











It is understood that in early August of this year, An Chenxi flew to Shanghai, originally intended to help her husband to celebrate Father's Day, and to meet with children, enjoy family fun, did not expect to fly to the local, her husband disappeared, then An Chenxi was blocked by Zhang Jia Outside the door, she was very anxious to see her children, so she called everyone in Zhang, but no one answered her. The children were even taken to the home of Zhang Xiaowei's brother.








What is even more heart-rending is that An Chenxi actually unexpectedly saw her husband’s extramarital sexual love photos and videos on this year’s birthday. There are also many intimate photos of her husband’s self-portraits and affair women. Zhang Zhang’s unbearable eyes make An Chen’s collapse completely. I know that my husband is not the person she knows.
Update time|2019.11.06 04:38
